## Test-Driven Development (mandatory)

> Every new feature, bugfix, or behavior change MUST follow Red ‚Üí Green ‚Üí Refactor:
> 1. **Red** ‚Äî write a failing test that demonstrates the desired behavior or reproduces the bug.
> 2. **Green** ‚Äî write the minimum production code to make the test pass.
> 3. **Refactor** ‚Äî clean up while keeping the bar green.
>
> PRs touching source files without corresponding test changes will be flagged by the `tdd-evidence` CI job (advisory in Phase 1, blocking from Phase 2).

