## When NOT to use TDD

Be honest: not every change needs a test.

- Pure dependency bumps (lockfile-only changes) ‚Äî no.
- Documentation-only changes (`*.md`, `README`, `docs/`) ‚Äî no.
- Pure tooling/config tweaks that have no runtime effect (e.g. editor settings, ignore-file additions) ‚Äî no.

Anything that touches behavior ‚Äî a route, a hook, a domain method, a schema, a model, a component's render output, a background task ‚Äî **does** need a test. If you're unsure, write one.

